Package: textometrieR
Type: Package
Title: Statistical exploration of textual corpora
Version: 0.5
Date: 2009-01-18
Author: Sylvain Loiseau, Vaudor Lise, Matthieu Decorde
Maintainer: Matthieu Decorde <matthieu.decorde@ens-lyon.fr>
Description: Statistical exploration of textual corpora using several methods
    from french 'lexiometrie' and french 'Data Analysis' schools. It includes
    methods for exploring irregularity of distribution of lexicon (or other
    features) accross parts of texts; multidimensionnal exploration ('Analyse
    des correspondances'), etc.
License: GPLv3
Depends: R (>= 2.5.0)
